snippet.title: Torchlight III - Sharpshooter Class Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
🏹 The Sharpshooter joins Torchlight III!

This unique class is all about precision shooting and summoning spirits. Combining distinct abilities with trinkets allows you to create custom builds that speak directly to your unique ranged playstyle.

Sign up for updates, exclusive content, beta tests, and more at https://www.Torchlight3.com

Like: https://www.facebook.com/PlayTorchlight 
Follow: https://twitter.com/PlayTorchlight 
Watch: https://www.twitch.tv/PlayTorchlight
Discuss: https://discordapp.com/invite/playtorchlight
